(5, 'big3', 'BIG 3', 'The Big 3 at Waves 2012- Where the highest stakes will be combined with the fiercest competition and the greatest joys. Where elegance, panache and X-factor will take control. And where there will be no room whatsoever for second best.'),
(6, 'dance', 'Dance', 'From the classical elan of Bharatnatyam to the spunk of the Western Streets, it all comes alive as you groove to the rythymic beats this year at Waves 2012, where you dance, and keep on dancing till the floors scream for mercy.'),
(7, 'music', 'Music', 'Tune your guitars, Set up your Bass Pedals and exercise your vocal chords for one of the most exciting Music extravaganza !! Gear up fpr Waves 2012- Relive the Streets.'),
(11, 'arts', 'Fine Arts', 'Grab your brushes! Open your paints, Finetune your sketching skills! And the most important of them all -- Your Creativity! Gear up for one of the best set of events at Waves-2012.'),
(12, 'ldc', 'Literary', 'Load your guns with the wittiest one-liners, the most deadly puns, the whackiest anagrams, the craziest arguements, and the most stinging insultsand fire them at your opponents to leave them with no thoughts to speak on, and no words to write.'),
(14, 'quiz', 'Quiz', 'If visual cues and neuron twisting questions lead to a sudden surge of impulses in your cerebral cortex, this is for you. This Waves, we are taking quizzing to an all new level. Do your best to find the elusive link and fill in the tantalising blanks.'),
(15, 'dramatics', 'Dramatics', '<p>The most alluring of life&#39;s rewards lies at the end of the tunnel. It is that which makes us work, day in and day out, dealing with many trials and tribulations on the way. All to catch the ultimate prize: to forsake who we are, and be who we&#39;ve alwa</p>'),
(16, 'searock', 'SeaRock', '<p>A sea of people. Wave after wave of cheers and chants come crashing and tumbling through the crisp night air and melt through the barriers of colour, caste and creed. For once, everyone will speak the same tongue. For once, it won&#39;t be about mind games and politics. For once, it will be a celebration of what is, and not what was. Come and experience the spectacle, as artist and audience unite to sing the same glorious song.</p>');

