(6, 'Official Pre-Sunbrun Event', 'sunburn', '<p>&nbsp;</p><div>This year at Waves we want our DJ Night&nbsp;to be a proper <strong>&lsquo;Pre-Sunburn Event&rsquo;</strong> &nbsp;with &nbsp;<strong>&lsquo;WAR OF THE DJs&rsquo; </strong></div><div>competition starting at noon, and leading upto a great&nbsp;headlining act post sundown, ensuring people will dance&nbsp;till they drop and be exposed to a true glimpse of <strong>&lsquo;THE SUNBURN EXPERIENCE&rsquo;&nbsp;</strong></div><div>&nbsp;</div>');

