INSERT INTO `pages` (`id`, `title`, `route`, `info`, `type`) VALUES
(1, 'The Events', 'events', 'Kick up your heels. Conjure up a storm. Whet your inquisitiveness. Unleash the Bard within. All the world''s a stage, it calls upon you to perform. Witness the coming together of the false Gods of the performing arts. Prove your mettle against the very finest. Or simply take pot-shots at your friends'' making a laughingstock of themselves. An eclectic mix of dazzling events awaits you this Waves, brace yourselves.', 1),
(2, 'Informals', 'informals', '<p>If you thought Waves was all about scheduled events and concerts lined up - you&rsquo;ve obviously overlooked our love for spontaneity! We bring to you the most fun activities to catch you off-guard- be it the evergreen housie, the impromptu &lsquo;minute-to-win-it&rsquo; tasks and the adrenaline rush of an all-night Treasure Hunt! If we tell you we&rsquo;re the proud recipients of a&nbsp; Limca Book Of Record title for &lsquo;Maximum number of people Arm Wrestling&rsquo;, would you like to join us for another record breaking act this Waves?</p>', 1),
(3, 'Specials', 'specials', 'The Waves Specials is that feature of this zany cult-fest which provides an exotic finishing touch to the biggest Fusion Festival of the year. Only at a festival that cherishes the celebration of Pure Milavat at every step can you have an array of colourful exhibitions, an immensely entertaining mob of fusion artists, and of course - the much awaited, much sought after Prom Night. The Waves Specials promise to bring the sheer joy of festivities straight to the very heart and soul of the hottest cult fest ever!', 1),
(4, 'Workshops', 'workshops', '<p>There is something for everybody at Waves! Are you a dance fanatic? Or the quintessential artist? Waves 2012 presents amazing array of workshops lined up which promise to live up to the fun quotient while being extremely engaging. Keeping up with the &lsquo;Street&rsquo; theme, have a world-renowned street dance group teach you the moves! Or sway to the titillating steps of Celebrity Belly dancer. For the artistically inclined, immerse yourself in the world of 3D Art or pick up your cameras for a workshop on Digital Matte technique. Regale the Chef in you while getting hands-on in a Cookery Workshop-taste bud delights guaranteed!</p>', 1),
(5, 'Nights', 'nights', '<p>It is only fair that the fervour and frenzy surrounding the day&rsquo;s events find due culmination in the Nights. This Waves, witness the mesmerizing might of Fusion being propagated by some of the very best in the business, as celebrated artists from all over the globe descend upon our very presence.</p>', 1),
