(1, 'Prom', 'prom', '<p>What&rsquo;s College life without the most looked forward to event-the college Ball? Let your hair down this Waves for we provide you the perfect occasion- the Waves Ball! With a partner for company, enjoy the mesmerizing ambience, the music, the dance&hellip;and top it off with lip-smacking food. This Waves we bring you a dash of the Middle East flavour and we bet &lsquo;Arabian Nights&rsquo; themed ball will sure make it to your most memorable evenings ever!</p>', 'a:2:{i:0;a:3:{s:4:\\"name\\";s:10:\\"Shashank S\\";s:5:\\"email\\";s:22:\\"sss.shashank@gmail.com\\";s:5:\\"phone\\";s:10:\\"9421350823\\";}i:1;a:3:{s:4:\\"name\\";s:10:\\"Priyanka U\\";s:5:\\"email\\";s:26:\\"priyankaunnithan@gmail.com\\";s:5:\\"phone\\";s:10:\\"8793532834\\";}}'),
(2, 'Adventure Zone', 'adventure', '<p>Waves 2012 boasts a variety of activities to satisfy the daredevil in you. And if that&rsquo;s coming from the organisers of the highly successful Paintball tournament &lsquo;Bazinga&rsquo; &amp; superbly entertaining &lsquo;Slip Futsal&rsquo;- you know we mean business. Do make sure you&rsquo;re a part of the most kick-ass events &amp; tournaments during the three-day extravaganza called Waves.</p>', 'a:2:{i:0;a:3:{s:4:\\"name\\";s:10:\\"Shashank S\\";s:5:\\"email\\";s:22:\\"sss.shashank@gmail.com\\";s:5:\\"phone\\";s:10:\\"9421350823\\";}i:1;a:3:{s:4:\\"name\\";s:10:\\"Priyanka U\\";s:5:\\"email\\";s:26:\\"priyankaunnithan@gmail.com\\";s:5:\\"phone\\";s:10:\\"8793532834\\";}}');

